HomeWiki:
Project Description
Very simple UITestPropertyProvider who handles the playback(Coded-UI Tests) of an dutch date for input-controls who are extended with MaskedEditExtender.

This is an simple implementation who checks an input control name ends with an predefined string.
When true the propertyprovider will do an alternative action.
